🚀 Azure Network Lab – Hub-Spoke Hybrid Architecture
📌 Overview

This lab demonstrates deployment of a secure Azure network architecture including:

Virtual Network with segmented subnets

Multiple Virtual Machines

Azure Load Balancer

Application Gateway (WAF)

Azure Firewall

Network Security Groups

Public IP configuration

Hybrid connectivity (VPN Gateway concept)

The objective was to simulate a real-world enterprise cloud network with traffic validation and segmentation controls.
